1
00:00:07,140 --> 00:00:08,474
♪

2
00:00:08,509 --> 00:00:10,410
( woman screams )

3
00:00:10,476 --> 00:00:15,015
Narrator: SEVEN YEARS LATER,
IN 1888...

4
00:00:16,416 --> 00:00:19,319
JACK THE RIPPER STALKED
THE STREETS OF LONDON,

5
00:00:19,352 --> 00:00:20,854
MURDERING WOMEN IN THE NIGHT

6
00:00:20,954 --> 00:00:23,690
AND HOLDING THE ENTIRE CITY
IN HIS THRALL.

7
00:00:23,790 --> 00:00:27,528
HOWEVER, HE WAS NOTHING
COMPARED TO THE HORROR

8
00:00:27,628 --> 00:00:30,163
THAT THE FEUD
BETWEEN JOJO AND DIO

9
00:00:30,196 --> 00:00:32,533
WOULD UNLEASH UPON THE WORLD.

10
00:00:35,301 --> 00:00:37,504
♪

11
00:00:45,211 --> 00:00:47,147
( singing in Japanese )

12
00:02:08,241 --> 00:02:10,143
♪

13
00:02:15,481 --> 00:02:17,316
Commentator: INTERCEPTION!

14
00:02:17,416 --> 00:02:19,886
THE BALL IS PLUCKED
OUT OF THE AIR

15
00:02:19,953 --> 00:02:23,724
BY OUR HERO, JONATHAN JOESTAR!

16
00:02:27,728 --> 00:02:30,964
JOESTAR, A GENTLE GIANT
AT 195 CENTIMETERS,

17
00:02:30,997 --> 00:02:34,668
SPRINTS FOR THE TRY ZONE
WITH A SPIRITED ROAR!

18
00:02:34,735 --> 00:02:38,238
CAN HE WIN THIS, THE LAST GAME
OF HIS UNIVERSITY CAREER?

19
00:02:38,304 --> 00:02:39,840
( player yells )

20
00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:42,442
Commentator:
HE'S TACKLED FROM BEHIND!

21
00:02:42,509 --> 00:02:44,611
WAIT! HE'S STILL STANDING TALL.

22
00:02:44,678 --> 00:02:45,612
( JoJo chuckles )

23
00:02:45,679 --> 00:02:47,581
Commentator: TWO MORE FLY IN.

24
00:02:47,648 --> 00:02:50,016
IT'S THREE ON ONE OUT THERE!

25
00:02:50,116 --> 00:02:52,653
( JoJo grunting )

26
00:02:52,686 --> 00:02:54,087
Player #2: HUH?

27
00:02:54,154 --> 00:02:55,088
Player #3: EH?

28
00:02:55,155 --> 00:02:57,624
Commentator: INCREDIBLE!

29
00:02:57,691 --> 00:02:59,926
HE'S STILL MAKING
FOR THE TRY LINE,

30
00:02:59,993 --> 00:03:02,769
UNDAUNTED BY THE MEN
WHO DOG HIS STEPS.

31
00:03:02,836 --> 00:03:06,873
WHAT POWER. WHAT DETERMINATION.
HE'S HERCULES REBORN.

32
00:03:06,940 --> 00:03:10,944
‐ ( player #4 yells )
‐ Commentator: ANOTHER TACKLE!

33
00:03:11,011 --> 00:03:14,047
OH, THE WEIGHT'S
TOO MUCH FOR HIM!

34
00:03:14,114 --> 00:03:15,048
( JoJo grunts )

35
00:03:15,115 --> 00:03:17,450
( yells )

36
00:03:17,518 --> 00:03:19,886
Commentator:
HE FLINGS IT AWAY, AND...

37
00:03:19,986 --> 00:03:22,188
YES! THERE'S THE CATCH.

38
00:03:22,222 --> 00:03:25,726
THE BALL LANDS SAFE
IN THE HANDS OF DIO BRANDO.

39
00:03:25,792 --> 00:03:27,961
IT'S STILL ANYONE'S GAME!

40
00:03:28,028 --> 00:03:30,396
( players yell )

41
00:03:30,463 --> 00:03:31,397
( both grunt )

42
00:03:31,464 --> 00:03:33,166
Commentator: CAN HE MAKE IT?

43
00:03:33,233 --> 00:03:36,236
HE DODGES ONE AND ANOTHER!

44
00:03:36,302 --> 00:03:37,671
HE'S DONE IT!

45
00:03:37,738 --> 00:03:39,840
THERE'S NOTHING LEFT
BETWEEN DIO AND THE TRY LINE,

46
00:03:39,906 --> 00:03:41,808
AND STILL HE GIVES IT HIS ALL.

47
00:03:41,875 --> 00:03:43,309
YES!

48
00:03:43,376 --> 00:03:44,310
( crowd cheering )

49
00:03:44,377 --> 00:03:46,079
Commentator: THEY DID IT!

50
00:03:46,179 --> 00:03:47,247
ON THE LAST PLAY,

51
00:03:47,313 --> 00:03:49,249
THEY SNATCHED VICTORY
OUT OF THE JAWS OF DEFEAT.

52
00:03:49,349 --> 00:03:52,485
WHAT TEAMWORK.
WHEN JOJO AND DIO WORK TOGETHER,

53
00:03:52,553 --> 00:03:55,255
THERE'S NOTHING THEY CAN'T DO.

54
00:03:55,355 --> 00:03:56,890
Dio: HELL OF A PASS, JOJO.

55
00:03:56,923 --> 00:03:59,593
JoJo: ALL FOR NAUGHT IF YOU
HADN'T RUN IT IN LIKE YOU DID.

56
00:03:59,660 --> 00:04:00,834
Dio: WATCHING YOU
DRAG THOSE DEFENDERS,

57
00:04:00,901 --> 00:04:02,536
I COULDN'T JUST LET YOU DOWN.

58
00:04:02,603 --> 00:04:04,037
Commentator:
HAVING FINISHED HIS STUDIES,

59
00:04:04,104 --> 00:04:07,107
DIO IS SET TO GRADUATE
WITH TOP MARKS IN LAW.

60
00:04:07,207 --> 00:04:10,376
JOJO, MEANWHILE,
HAS SET THE FACULTY AFIRE

61
00:04:10,443 --> 00:04:12,913
WITH HIS BOLD THESIS
ON ARCHEOLOGY.

62
00:04:12,946 --> 00:04:16,717
ON AND OFF THE FIELD,
THESE TWO YOUNG MEN ARE GIANTS.

63
00:04:16,783 --> 00:04:18,719
THEY'RE THE PRIDE
OF OUR SCHOOL.

64
00:04:18,785 --> 00:04:21,121
Dio: JOJO, I THINK
WE SHOULD TELL OUR FATHER

65
00:04:21,221 --> 00:04:23,289
ABOUT THIS VICTORY OF OURS
AT ONCE.

66
00:04:23,389 --> 00:04:24,290
( JoJo grunts )

67
00:04:29,062 --> 00:04:31,765
IT'S BEEN SEVEN YEARS NOW

68
00:04:31,798 --> 00:04:34,601
SINCE MY FATHER
WELCOMED DIO INTO OUR HOME,

69
00:04:34,634 --> 00:04:37,036
SEVEN LONG YEARS.

70
00:04:37,103 --> 00:04:39,773
I SMILE AND TREAT HIM
AS A BROTHER,

71
00:04:39,806 --> 00:04:43,309
BUT IN MY HEART, NOTHING COULD
BE FURTHER FROM THE TRUTH.

72
00:04:43,376 --> 00:04:46,947
HE'S NOTHING IF NOT AFFABLE
AND SMART AS A WHIP...

73
00:04:50,551 --> 00:04:54,788
BUT I JUST CAN'T FORGIVE HIM
FOR HIS EARLY VILLAINIES.

74
00:04:54,821 --> 00:04:57,323
Reporter: DIO,
MIGHTN'T YOU GIVE US A QUOTE

75
00:04:57,390 --> 00:04:58,725
ABOUT YOUR FRIENDSHIP WITH JOJO?

76
00:04:58,792 --> 00:04:59,993
YOU SEEM QUITE CLOSE.

77
00:05:00,060 --> 00:05:02,669
Dio: WRITE ABOUT THE TEAM,
ALL OF US.

78
00:05:02,736 --> 00:05:05,338
Man: COME ON.
TELL US HOW CLOSE YOU ARE.

79
00:05:05,405 --> 00:05:06,773
Dio: HMM. SHOULD I?

80
00:05:07,674 --> 00:05:08,742
HEH.

81
00:05:08,809 --> 00:05:10,410
FRIENDSHIP, HUH?

82
00:05:10,476 --> 00:05:14,648
THE TRUTH IS I DESPISE
THIS GRINNING IMBECILE.

83
00:05:14,681 --> 00:05:16,182
I'VE SPENT SEVEN YEARS

84
00:05:16,282 --> 00:05:19,285
MAKING NICE
TO THAT JOESTAR BRAT,

85
00:05:19,352 --> 00:05:21,522
BUT NOW THAT I AM OF AGE,

86
00:05:21,622 --> 00:05:24,024
I SHALL BRING
MY PLANS TO FRUITION.

87
00:05:24,124 --> 00:05:27,761
AT LONG LAST, THE JOESTAR
FORTUNE WILL BE MINE,

88
00:05:27,828 --> 00:05:31,364
AND DEVIL TAKE
ANYONE WHO TRIES TO STOP ME.

89
00:05:31,464 --> 00:05:34,034
( man coughing )

90
00:05:35,869 --> 00:05:38,605
Dio: FATHER,
HOW ARE YOU FEELING TODAY?

91
00:05:38,672 --> 00:05:43,143
George: BUT FOR THIS COUGH,
MUCH IMPROVED OVER YESTERDAY.

92
00:05:43,209 --> 00:05:44,210
( coughs )

93
00:05:44,277 --> 00:05:47,213
THE DOCTORS SAY
I SHOULD BE IN THE HOSPITAL.

94
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:50,150
Dio: WHY? I FEAR
IT WOULD DO YOU NO GOOD.

95
00:05:50,216 --> 00:05:52,953
HOSPITALS ONLY CARE
ABOUT PROFIT.

96
00:05:53,019 --> 00:05:56,690
THEY'D MEASURE YOU FOR A SHROUD
ERE THEY SAW YOU CURED.

97
00:05:56,723 --> 00:05:58,992
George: HMM.
THEN HERE I SHALL REMAIN.

98
00:05:59,059 --> 00:06:01,802
THE COMFORTS OF HOME
ARE CURATIVE, LIKE AS NOT.

99
00:06:01,868 --> 00:06:07,708
MY CHEST DOESN'T PAIN ME SO,
AND THE SWELLING HAS GONE DOWN.

100
00:06:07,741 --> 00:06:08,842
I'M ON THE MEND.

101
00:06:08,909 --> 00:06:10,977
‐ ( coughs )
‐ JoJo: IT WAS JUST A COLD.

102
00:06:11,044 --> 00:06:12,646
WHY HAS IT WORSENED SO?

103
00:06:12,713 --> 00:06:15,315
George: I HEARD TELL
OF YOUR VICTORY.

104
00:06:15,381 --> 00:06:16,817
STUNNING BIT OF TEAMWORK.

105
00:06:16,883 --> 00:06:18,985
JoJo: SOMEONE
TOLD YOU ABOUT IT?

106
00:06:19,052 --> 00:06:22,255
George: I GOT WORD STRAIGHTAWAY
FROM AN OLD COLLEGE CHUM.

107
00:06:22,322 --> 00:06:24,190
Dio: WHOEVER HE IS, HE'S FAST.

108
00:06:24,257 --> 00:06:26,426
I'M GLAD HE WASN'T
ON OUR OPPONENTS' TEAM,

109
00:06:26,527 --> 00:06:27,528
OR WE COULD HAVE LOST.

110
00:06:27,594 --> 00:06:29,095
( both laughing )

111
00:06:29,162 --> 00:06:31,097
George: I'M PROUD OF YOU, LADS.

112
00:06:31,164 --> 00:06:33,433
YOU BOTH TURNED OUT SO WELL.

113
00:06:33,534 --> 00:06:34,935
PROVIDENCE IS TOO KIND.

114
00:06:35,035 --> 00:06:38,104
DIO, I'M SO GLAD YOU'VE THRIVED.

115
00:06:38,171 --> 00:06:41,341
PURSUE YOUR AMBITIONS,
WHATEVER THEY MAY BE.

116
00:06:41,407 --> 00:06:45,779
I WILL LEND YOU AID
IN ANY WAY I CAN, MY SON.

117
00:06:45,846 --> 00:06:48,014
Dio: YOU RESCUED ME
FROM CALAMITY.

118
00:06:48,081 --> 00:06:51,451
ALREADY MY DEBT IS MORE
THAN I CAN EVER REPAY.

119
00:06:51,552 --> 00:06:54,287
YOU DO ME TOO MUCH HONOR.

120
00:06:54,387 --> 00:06:56,422
♪

121
00:07:08,308 --> 00:07:10,944
JoJo: THIS SECRET IS MINE ALONE.

122
00:07:10,977 --> 00:07:13,046
I CAN'T IMAGINE FOR WHAT PURPOSE

123
00:07:13,113 --> 00:07:16,049
THIS MASK MAY HAVE
BEEN FASHIONED OR BY WHOM,

124
00:07:16,116 --> 00:07:17,984
BUT IT BELONGED TO MY MOTHER,

125
00:07:18,084 --> 00:07:20,654
AND SO HAVING IT NEAR
IS A COMFORT,

126
00:07:20,721 --> 00:07:22,155
STRANGE AS THAT MAY SEEM.

127
00:07:22,222 --> 00:07:26,159
WHEN I FINALLY OUTWIT
THIS SPHINX OF A MASK,

128
00:07:26,226 --> 00:07:29,563
IT WILL BE THE TALK
OF THE ARCHEOLOGICAL WORLD.

129
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:31,331
MY GOODNESS!

130
00:07:37,504 --> 00:07:40,774
Butler: MANY THANKS TO YOU,
MASTER DIO.

131
00:07:40,841 --> 00:07:42,509
THE YEARS BETRAY ME.

132
00:07:42,576 --> 00:07:46,112
CLIMBING THE STAIRS IS
MUCH HARDER THAN IT WAS BEFORE.

133
00:07:47,648 --> 00:07:48,982
JoJo: THIS LETTER,

134
00:07:49,015 --> 00:07:52,519
HAVING READ IT,
ALL HAS BEEN MADE CLEAR.

135
00:07:53,654 --> 00:07:54,855
DIO...

136
00:07:55,856 --> 00:07:57,624
I THINK HE'S...

137
00:07:57,691 --> 00:08:00,366
( Dio chuckles )

138
00:08:01,768 --> 00:08:04,170
♪

139
00:08:05,205 --> 00:08:06,372
JoJo: DIO!

140
00:08:06,472 --> 00:08:08,341
WAIT. THAT'S‐‐

141
00:08:08,374 --> 00:08:11,211
THAT'S FATHER'S MEDICINE.

142
00:08:13,514 --> 00:08:15,616
Dio: HE'S DUE
FOR HIS NEXT DOSAGE.

143
00:08:15,682 --> 00:08:17,017
JoJo: ALL THIS TIME,

144
00:08:17,050 --> 00:08:19,553
YOU'RE THE ONE
WHO'S BEEN BRINGING IT TO HIM.

145
00:08:19,653 --> 00:08:20,654
Dio: YES. WHAT OF IT?

146
00:08:20,721 --> 00:08:21,888
JoJo: THIS LETTER,

147
00:08:21,988 --> 00:08:24,124
YOUR FATHER SENT IT TO MINE.

148
00:08:24,190 --> 00:08:25,626
GUESS WHAT IT SAYS.

149
00:08:25,692 --> 00:08:29,062
"YOUR LORDSHIP,
SICKNESS HAS LAID ME RIGHT LOW.

150
00:08:29,129 --> 00:08:32,398
"IT'S THE END OF ME,
WHATEVER IT IS.

151
00:08:32,498 --> 00:08:34,134
"MY CHEST HURTS,

152
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:36,036
"MY FINGERS'RE ALL SWOLE UP,

153
00:08:36,069 --> 00:08:38,404
AND I CAN'T BREATHE,
BUT FOR ALL THIS COUGHING."

154
00:08:38,505 --> 00:08:41,808
THOSE ARE THE SAME SYMPTOMS
AS FATHER'S, BLOW FOR BLOW!

155
00:08:41,875 --> 00:08:43,744
NO WAY IS THIS
MERE COINCIDENCE.

156
00:08:43,810 --> 00:08:44,911
DIO!

157
00:08:44,978 --> 00:08:47,247
Dio: WHAT ARE YOU
TRYING TO SAY, JOJO?

158
00:08:47,313 --> 00:08:50,216
JoJo: I'M HAVING A DOCTOR
LOOK AT THIS POWDER.

159
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:56,857
Dio: JOJO, IF YOU THINK
I WOULD POISON FATHER,

160
00:08:56,923 --> 00:08:59,760
THEN FROM THIS DAY FORWARD,
YOU AND I...

161
00:08:59,826 --> 00:09:01,067
ARE FRIENDS NO MORE!

162
00:09:01,101 --> 00:09:03,236
( JoJo gasping )

163
00:09:03,269 --> 00:09:06,339
TRY AS I MIGHT,
I CAN'T LOOK DIO IN THE EYE.

164
00:09:06,406 --> 00:09:07,841
IT'S BECAUSE I LACK PROOF.

165
00:09:07,908 --> 00:09:10,443
ALL I HAVE TO GO ON
ARE MY SUSPICIONS.

166
00:09:10,511 --> 00:09:14,615
Dio: NOW, THEN, IF YOU PUT
THAT MEDICINE BACK ON THE TRAY,

167
00:09:14,681 --> 00:09:18,552
I'LL BE WILLING TO FORGET
ABOUT YOUR LAPSE IN JUDGMENT.

168
00:09:20,353 --> 00:09:21,555
JoJo: DIO,

169
00:09:21,622 --> 00:09:23,690
THERE'S ONLY ONE WAY
YOU'RE GOING TO CONVINCE ME.

170
00:09:23,757 --> 00:09:26,226
SWEAR TO ME THAT
THE CONTENTS OF THIS ARE SAFE.

171
00:09:26,292 --> 00:09:27,594
DO IT IN DARIO'S NAME.

172
00:09:27,628 --> 00:09:30,296
SWEAR TO ME ON DARIO'S HONOR
AS A GENTLEMAN.

173
00:09:30,363 --> 00:09:32,799
DO THAT, AND I'LL NEVER
BRING UP THIS MOMENT AGAIN.

174
00:09:32,899 --> 00:09:34,267
( Dio gasps )

175
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:37,303
JoJo: IF MY HUNCH PROVES TRUE,
HIS FATHER'S HONOR

176
00:09:37,370 --> 00:09:40,473
IS THE ONE LIE
THAT WILL CATCH IN HIS THROAT.

177
00:09:40,574 --> 00:09:43,577
SAY IT!
WHAT ARE YOU WAITING FOR?

178
00:09:43,644 --> 00:09:47,047
Dio: I S‐SWEAR...

179
00:09:48,214 --> 00:09:52,218
HOW CAN I SWEAR
ON THE HONOR OF A MAN

180
00:09:52,285 --> 00:09:53,954
WHO DIDN'T HAVE ANY?!

181
00:09:53,987 --> 00:09:55,556
HE DESERVED TO DIE!

182
00:09:55,622 --> 00:09:58,091
HOW'S THAT
FOR THE TRUTH, JOJO?!

183
00:10:00,460 --> 00:10:04,070
JoJo: YOU JUST GAVE ME
ALL THE PROOF I NEEDED, DIO.

184
00:10:04,104 --> 00:10:06,840
AT HEARING HIS NAME,
YOU LASHED OUT.

185
00:10:06,907 --> 00:10:09,342
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT HE COULD HAVE DONE

186
00:10:09,409 --> 00:10:11,211
THAT MOVED YOU
TO SUCH MURDEROUS RAGE,

187
00:10:11,277 --> 00:10:13,514
BUT MURDER HIM, YOU SURELY DID.

188
00:10:16,016 --> 00:10:18,585
( Dio gasping )

189
00:10:18,619 --> 00:10:20,687
YOU HURT FATHER.

190
00:10:20,754 --> 00:10:22,122
NEVER AGAIN, DIO.

191
00:10:27,393 --> 00:10:28,461
( Dio groans )

192
00:10:30,631 --> 00:10:32,465
DAMN YOUR EYES.

193
00:10:33,634 --> 00:10:34,768
JoJo: OF COURSE.

194
00:10:34,801 --> 00:10:37,303
YOU'VE BEEN PLANNING
TO MURDER HIM FOR YEARS NOW.

195
00:10:37,370 --> 00:10:40,874
I KNEW IT. I KNEW THAT YOU
WERE PLAYING FALSE WITH US.

196
00:10:40,941 --> 00:10:42,943
BUT NOW YOUR VILLAINY IS OVER.

197
00:10:42,976 --> 00:10:44,945
ONCE I'VE LEARNED WHAT THIS IS,

198
00:10:44,978 --> 00:10:47,548
I'M TAKING IT
TO THE POLICE STRAIGHTAWAY.

199
00:10:47,614 --> 00:10:49,282
( Dio sputters )

200
00:10:50,383 --> 00:10:51,217
DAMN IT.

201
00:10:51,284 --> 00:10:53,954
THEIR FORTUNE
WAS WITHIN MY GRASP.

202
00:10:53,987 --> 00:10:57,758
WAS IT FATE THAT JOJO
FOUND OUT WHEN HE DID?

203
00:10:57,824 --> 00:11:00,801
NO. IT WAS THAT LETTER.

204
00:11:00,834 --> 00:11:03,336
HE VEXES ME EVEN NOW.

205
00:11:03,436 --> 00:11:06,507
Dario: YOU'RE WEAK,
JUST LIKE YOUR MOTHER!

206
00:11:06,607 --> 00:11:09,342
Dio: HE DROVE HER
TO AN EARLY GRAVE.

207
00:11:09,442 --> 00:11:13,346
KNOWING THAT CUR'S BLOOD
FLOWS THROUGH MY VEINS,

208
00:11:13,413 --> 00:11:15,348
IT'S ENOUGH TO DRIVE ME MAD!

209
00:11:15,448 --> 00:11:17,350
♪

210
00:11:20,654 --> 00:11:24,758
SIR JOESTAR LIVES FOR NOW.

211
00:11:33,266 --> 00:11:36,770
JoJo: I'LL BE BACK FROM LONDON
IN A FEW DAYS, FATHER.

212
00:11:36,837 --> 00:11:40,774
'TIL THEN, ACCEPT MEDICINE ONLY
FROM THE HANDS OF THESE DOCTORS

213
00:11:40,841 --> 00:11:42,375
AND NO ONE ELSE.

214
00:11:42,442 --> 00:11:46,346
Butler: MASTER JOJO SAID HE
DOESN'T WANT ME TO BRING IT UP?

215
00:11:46,379 --> 00:11:49,716
George: YES. WE WILL DO
AS JOJO HAS INSTRUCTED US.

216
00:11:51,117 --> 00:11:53,386
HIS REASONS ARE A MYSTERY TO ME,

217
00:11:53,453 --> 00:11:56,557
BUT I TRUST THE BOY
WITH MY LIFE. ( coughs )

218
00:11:56,657 --> 00:11:59,225
JoJo: THANK YOU, FATHER.

219
00:11:59,325 --> 00:12:01,902
HIS ILLNESS IS GETTING WORSE.

220
00:12:02,002 --> 00:12:03,637
( horses galloping )

221
00:12:03,704 --> 00:12:07,541
IF IT IS A POISON,
HE MAY NEED AN ANTIDOTE.

222
00:12:08,675 --> 00:12:11,244
♪

223
00:12:11,311 --> 00:12:14,414
Dio: WHATEVER YOU MAY LEARN
IN LONDON ABOUT THE POISON,

224
00:12:14,515 --> 00:12:18,084
I'LL SEE YOU TAKE
THE TRUTH OF IT TO YOUR GRAVE.

225
00:12:18,184 --> 00:12:22,088
YOUR DEATH WILL BE
THE PERFECT CRIME.

226
00:12:22,188 --> 00:12:25,926
SEVEN YEARS AGO,
THIS MASK REACTED TO MY BLOOD.

227
00:12:25,992 --> 00:12:30,931
THE SPIKES HIDDEN WITHIN WILL
MAKE SHORT WORK OF JOJO'S BRAIN.

228
00:12:31,031 --> 00:12:32,766
HIS INJURIES WILL BE SO UNIQUE,

229
00:12:32,833 --> 00:12:36,236
THERE'LL BE NOTHING AT ALL
TO TIE IT BACK TO ME.

230
00:12:36,269 --> 00:12:42,208
JOJO, YOUR CURIOSITY
WILL LEAD TO YOUR DESTRUCTION.

231
00:12:43,276 --> 00:12:46,446
‐ Driver: WHOA. WHOA.
‐ ( horses neigh )

232
00:12:46,547 --> 00:12:51,217
JoJo: THE UNIVERSITY COULDN'T
IDENTIFY THE SO‐CALLED MEDICINE,

233
00:12:51,284 --> 00:12:52,452
THOUGH THEY DID SPECULATE

234
00:12:52,553 --> 00:12:55,188
THAT IT WAS A COMPOUND
FROM THE ORIENT.

235
00:12:56,189 --> 00:12:57,390
THEREFORE...

236
00:12:57,457 --> 00:12:58,625
Driver: YOUNG MASTER,

237
00:12:58,692 --> 00:13:01,134
THAT STRETCH OF ROAD THERE
IS OGRE STREET,

238
00:13:01,234 --> 00:13:03,403
THE MOST DANGEROUS ALLEYWAY
IN ALL OF LONDON.

239
00:13:03,469 --> 00:13:06,206
JoJo: YES, I KNOW,
BUT THIS IS THE ONE PLACE

240
00:13:06,272 --> 00:13:08,609
I WILL BE ABLE TO FIND
WHAT I CAME FOR.

241
00:13:08,642 --> 00:13:10,210
YOU'RE MORE THAN WELCOME
TO LEAVE.

242
00:13:10,276 --> 00:13:11,411
Driver: HMM?

243
00:13:12,312 --> 00:13:14,047
JoJo: DIO GREW UP IN LONDON.

244
00:13:14,114 --> 00:13:17,984
WHERE ELSE IN ENGLAND COULD HE
HAVE ACQUIRED SUCH A TOXIN?

245
00:13:18,084 --> 00:13:19,820
I SHALL HAVE MY EVIDENCE...

246
00:13:19,886 --> 00:13:22,422
AND FATHER'S ANTIDOTE.

247
00:13:22,488 --> 00:13:24,625
♪

248
00:13:24,658 --> 00:13:26,593
ANOTHER DEAD END.

249
00:13:30,396 --> 00:13:31,798
( cat screeches )

250
00:13:31,832 --> 00:13:33,600
( JoJo gasps ) THAT CAT...

251
00:13:33,667 --> 00:13:36,603
‐ IT WAS EATING A PUPPY.
‐ ( man whistles )

252
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:39,506
♪

253
00:13:39,573 --> 00:13:41,141
Man: YOU DO THE HONORS, TATTOO.

254
00:13:41,174 --> 00:13:42,475
Tattoo: RIGHT!

255
00:13:42,509 --> 00:13:45,111
Man: USE THAT SHIV OF YOURS
TO SLICE HIM OPEN.

256
00:13:45,178 --> 00:13:47,147
I WANT HIS GUTS FOR GARTERS!

257
00:13:47,180 --> 00:13:50,250
JoJo: OGRE STREET.
IT IS APTLY NAMED.

258
00:13:51,284 --> 00:13:52,853
( Tattoo screams )

259
00:13:54,688 --> 00:13:55,656
( chuckles )

260
00:13:56,857 --> 00:13:57,858
CHECK OUT THIS IDIOT!

261
00:13:57,958 --> 00:13:59,192
HE GRABBED MY BLADE!

262
00:13:59,259 --> 00:14:01,868
IN ALL MY DAYS,
I'VE NEVER SEEN THE LIKE.

263
00:14:01,968 --> 00:14:03,804
HA HA HA! STUCK, AIN'T YA?

264
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:05,939
ONE QUICK YANK OF THE KNIFE,
AND THEY'LL BE

265
00:14:06,006 --> 00:14:08,509
PICKING YOUR FINGERS
OUT OF THE SNOW FOR A FORTNIGHT.

266
00:14:08,542 --> 00:14:10,711
JoJo: TRY IT, THEN.
THE MOMENT YOU PULL,

267
00:14:10,777 --> 00:14:13,179
MY FOOT WILL KICK OUT
AT YOUR GROIN

268
00:14:13,213 --> 00:14:15,448
WITH ALL THE FORCE
OF A SLEDGEHAMMER.

269
00:14:15,516 --> 00:14:17,784
I'M WILLING TO SEE
OUR TRANSACTION THROUGH.

270
00:14:17,851 --> 00:14:18,719
ARE YOU, SIRRAH?

271
00:14:18,785 --> 00:14:20,521
I'M FIGHTING
TO PROTECT MY FAMILY

272
00:14:20,554 --> 00:14:22,055
FROM THOSE WHO WISH IT HARM.

273
00:14:22,122 --> 00:14:25,125
I DOUBT VERY MUCH THAT
YOUR RESOLVE IS EQUAL TO MINE.

274
00:14:25,191 --> 00:14:26,860
( man #2 yells )

275
00:14:29,563 --> 00:14:30,997
JoJo: THAT'S QUITE ENOUGH.

276
00:14:31,064 --> 00:14:32,666
NOW TELL ME, ONE OF YOU,

277
00:14:32,733 --> 00:14:34,835
WHERE CAN I FIND
AN ASIAN APOTHECARY?

278
00:14:34,901 --> 00:14:35,869
Man #1: TOUGH TALK.

279
00:14:35,902 --> 00:14:37,871
IF YOU'RE LOOKING
TO LOSE BODY PARTS,

280
00:14:37,904 --> 00:14:40,240
DO STICK AROUND.

281
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:42,008
OBSERVE.

282
00:14:42,075 --> 00:14:44,745
( metal clinks )

283
00:14:44,811 --> 00:14:45,979
( JoJo gasps )

284
00:14:47,413 --> 00:14:49,816
Man #1: I'LL MINCE YA
RIGHT FINELY

285
00:14:49,883 --> 00:14:51,752
WITH A TIP OF THE HAT.

286
00:14:53,854 --> 00:14:56,256
AND NOW, WE DANCE.

287
00:14:56,356 --> 00:14:58,424
JoJo: I HAVE TO FIND
THAT APOTHECARY,

288
00:14:58,491 --> 00:14:59,660
NO MATTER THE COST.

289
00:14:59,726 --> 00:15:01,434
Man #1: DON'T TELL ME
THIS HERE'S

290
00:15:01,535 --> 00:15:03,103
YOUR FIRST PROPER DUST‐UP.

291
00:15:03,169 --> 00:15:06,740
IF YOU MEAN TO BLOCK LIKE THAT,
IT'LL BE YOUR LAST ONE, TOO.

292
00:15:11,945 --> 00:15:12,879
HA HA!

293
00:15:12,946 --> 00:15:14,848
CUT YA STRAIGHT TO THE BONE,
LOOKS LIKE.

294
00:15:14,915 --> 00:15:17,784
GRANTED, I DIDN'T THINK YOU'D
HOOF THE SHIV AT ME LIKE THAT,

295
00:15:17,851 --> 00:15:19,953
BUT MY CHAPEAU
STILL HIT ITS MARK.

296
00:15:20,020 --> 00:15:22,288
♪

297
00:15:25,258 --> 00:15:29,362
NOW I KNOW WHY HE WEREN'T
DEFENDING HIMSELF BETTER.

298
00:15:29,429 --> 00:15:30,731
FINGERS, HANDS, LEGS,

299
00:15:30,797 --> 00:15:33,133
HE DON'T CARE
ONE WHIT WHAT HE LOSES.

300
00:15:33,199 --> 00:15:36,570
IT'S AS IF HIS RESOLVE
RUNS DEEPER THAN PAIN OR FEAR.

301
00:15:36,637 --> 00:15:39,439
I TOOK THE LAD FOR AN EASY MARK.

302
00:15:39,472 --> 00:15:42,576
GUESS I'VE BEEN RIGHT DISABUSED
OF THAT NOTION.

303
00:15:44,811 --> 00:15:47,280
♪

304
00:15:47,313 --> 00:15:50,050
( men murmuring, chuckling )

305
00:15:52,385 --> 00:15:55,656
Dio: WHAT? JOJO WENT
TO OGRE STREET ON HIS OWN?

306
00:15:55,756 --> 00:15:58,158
Driver: I TOLD HIM
IT WAS PERILOUS.

307
00:15:58,224 --> 00:15:59,660
Dio: KEEP THIS TO YOURSELF.

308
00:15:59,726 --> 00:16:01,768
SIR JOESTAR IS STILL UNWELL.

309
00:16:01,835 --> 00:16:03,003
Driver: YES, SIR.

310
00:16:03,103 --> 00:16:06,507
Dio: I GUESS I WON'T NEED
TO USE THE MASK AFTER ALL.

311
00:16:06,607 --> 00:16:09,943
THERE, ALONE?
HIS FATE IS SEALED.

312
00:16:10,010 --> 00:16:13,079
( men laughing )

313
00:16:13,146 --> 00:16:14,347
Man #1: THAT'S ENOUGH, LADS!

314
00:16:14,447 --> 00:16:16,850
I WON'T LET A SINGLE ONE OF YA

315
00:16:16,917 --> 00:16:19,185
LAY A FINGER
ON THAT GENTLEMAN THERE.

316
00:16:19,252 --> 00:16:21,254
( JoJo gasps )
BUT WHY?

317
00:16:21,321 --> 00:16:22,989
Man #1: TELL ME SOMETHING.

318
00:16:23,023 --> 00:16:25,291
STRONG AS A BULL, YOU ARE.

319
00:16:25,358 --> 00:16:26,693
IT'S PLAIN TO SEE.

320
00:16:26,760 --> 00:16:29,429
YOU COULDA STOVE MY HEAD IN
WITH THAT FOOT OF YOURS,

321
00:16:29,495 --> 00:16:31,331
BUT YOU WENT EASY ON ME,
DIDN'T YOU?

322
00:16:31,364 --> 00:16:32,866
( men gasp )

323
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:37,170
JoJo: I CAME HERE
FOR THE SAKE OF MY FATHER.

324
00:16:37,203 --> 00:16:38,672
YOU HAVE A FAMILY,

325
00:16:38,705 --> 00:16:41,675
PEOPLE WHO EXPECT YOU TO RETURN
FROM THIS DARK BUSINESS.

326
00:16:41,708 --> 00:16:45,311
IT IS NOT MY PLACE
TO CAUSE THEM GRIEF.

327
00:16:45,378 --> 00:16:47,548
Man #1: HE MEANS IT, DON'T HE?

328
00:16:47,614 --> 00:16:49,683
HOW'D THIS FELLA
SURVIVE SO LONG?

329
00:16:49,716 --> 00:16:51,051
WAIT.

330
00:16:52,553 --> 00:16:56,957
HE SPARED MY MATES' LIVES,
JUST LIKE HE DID MINE.

331
00:16:57,023 --> 00:16:59,960
I LIKE THE CUT OF HIS JIB.
SURE, HE'S NA ÏVE,

332
00:17:00,026 --> 00:17:02,736
BUT HE'S A GENTLEMAN
THROUGH AN' THROUGH, THIS ONE.

333
00:17:02,836 --> 00:17:05,706
I WANNA KNOW THE NAME
OF HIM WHO SPARED ME.

334
00:17:06,740 --> 00:17:08,909
JoJo: JONATHAN JOESTAR.

335
00:17:09,009 --> 00:17:11,745
Man #1: WELL, PLEASED
TO MAKE YOUR ACQUAINTANCE.

336
00:17:11,845 --> 00:17:14,314
IF IT'S ASIAN CONCOCTIONS
YOU'RE LOOKING FOR,

337
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:15,582
MIND YOUR BACK.

338
00:17:15,682 --> 00:17:17,751
THAT DRUGGIST
IS ONE SLY CUSTOMER.

339
00:17:17,851 --> 00:17:23,690
Doctor: SIR JOESTAR,
JOJO'S BEEN GONE THREE DAYS.

340
00:17:23,757 --> 00:17:25,826
George: WHATEVER HIS ERRAND,
HE'LL ACCOMPLISH IT.

341
00:17:25,892 --> 00:17:28,695
Doctor: HEH. WHERE HAVE
THE YEARS GONE, I WONDER?

342
00:17:28,762 --> 00:17:30,396
HE'S GROWN INTO A FINE MAN.

343
00:17:30,430 --> 00:17:31,932
George: I CANNOT HELP BUT WONDER

344
00:17:31,998 --> 00:17:34,835
IF I WAS TOO HARD
ON THE BOY GROWING UP.

345
00:17:41,508 --> 00:17:43,343
( cat hisses )

346
00:17:43,409 --> 00:17:45,779
( Dio groans )

347
00:17:47,848 --> 00:17:52,052
I'M SURE JOJO'S LAYING DEAD
IN SOME ALLEY BY NOW.

348
00:17:52,118 --> 00:17:54,120
DID HE FIND THE APOTHECARY?

349
00:17:54,220 --> 00:17:57,858
LOOK AT ME. SWILLING IT DOWN.

350
00:17:57,924 --> 00:18:02,068
NOTHING BUT A DRUNKEN FOOL,
JUST LIKE MY BASTARD FATHER.

351
00:18:02,135 --> 00:18:03,236
DAMN IT!

352
00:18:03,303 --> 00:18:05,872
( man laughs )

353
00:18:05,939 --> 00:18:06,940
WATCH YOURSELF!

354
00:18:06,973 --> 00:18:10,644
OR HAVE YOU NO RESPECT
FOR YOUR ELDERS, BOY?

355
00:18:10,744 --> 00:18:12,946
LOOK AT THE BABY
TODDLING AROUND PAST BEDTIME,

356
00:18:12,979 --> 00:18:16,149
SUCKING ON A BOTTLE
LIKE IT WAS HIS MOTHER'S TEAT.

357
00:18:16,216 --> 00:18:17,317
( man #2 laughs )

358
00:18:17,417 --> 00:18:19,052
LOOK AT THE MAN
WHEN HE'S TALKING.

359
00:18:19,119 --> 00:18:21,121
DIDN'T YOUR OLD MAN
TEACH YOU RIGHT?

360
00:18:22,789 --> 00:18:24,725
‐ ( man #1 wails )
‐ Man #2: MY GOD.

361
00:18:24,791 --> 00:18:27,761
JUST FOR THAT, I'M GONNA
TAKE YOUR FACE CLEAN OFF YA.

362
00:18:27,828 --> 00:18:31,397
Dio: OH. YOUR THREAT
HAS ME QUAKING IN MY BOOTS,

363
00:18:31,464 --> 00:18:32,666
YOU OLD GUTTERSNIPE.

364
00:18:32,766 --> 00:18:36,837
HOW WILL I ESCAPE
THIS MOMENT OF MORTAL PERIL?

365
00:18:36,903 --> 00:18:38,138
HOW ABOUT...

366
00:18:38,171 --> 00:18:40,140
WE USE THIS?

367
00:18:40,173 --> 00:18:42,008
IT'S MEANT FOR JOJO,

368
00:18:42,075 --> 00:18:44,477
BUT YOU'LL MAKE
A FINE GUINEA PIG.

369
00:18:44,511 --> 00:18:46,146
Man #2: JUST DIE ALREADY!

370
00:18:46,179 --> 00:18:47,648
EH?

371
00:18:47,681 --> 00:18:50,450
Dio: LET'S SEE WHAT YOU CAN DO!

372
00:18:50,517 --> 00:18:53,086
( man #1 gasping )

373
00:18:59,526 --> 00:19:01,101
( Dio gasps )

374
00:19:01,167 --> 00:19:03,036
W‐WHAT IS THAT LIGHT?

375
00:19:15,716 --> 00:19:18,284
ALL OF THAT SPECTACLE
FOR NOTHING?

376
00:19:18,351 --> 00:19:20,554
USELESS.

377
00:19:20,621 --> 00:19:21,555
( spits )

378
00:19:21,622 --> 00:19:22,556
THAT WAS BORING.

379
00:19:22,623 --> 00:19:25,726
I EXPECTED MORE FROM YOU, MASK.

380
00:19:30,396 --> 00:19:31,898
( wipes hat )

381
00:19:31,965 --> 00:19:33,900
♪

382
00:19:39,673 --> 00:19:41,074
( gasps )

383
00:19:41,174 --> 00:19:42,743
IMPOSSIBLE.

384
00:19:45,679 --> 00:19:48,214
HE'S ALIVE.

385
00:19:50,851 --> 00:19:53,654
THAT FACE. THOSE TEETH.

386
00:19:53,720 --> 00:19:55,889
‐ ( creature hisses )
‐ Dio: NO!

387
00:19:58,725 --> 00:20:00,701
( creature shrieks )

388
00:20:06,206 --> 00:20:07,173
( creature shrieks )

389
00:20:07,207 --> 00:20:08,875
Dio: WHAT INCREDIBLE STRENGTH.

390
00:20:11,512 --> 00:20:14,815
( groans )

391
00:20:16,850 --> 00:20:19,319
EVEN NOW, HE ADVANCES.

392
00:20:19,385 --> 00:20:20,721
BUT HIS HAND...

393
00:20:20,787 --> 00:20:22,055
DOES THE PAIN MEAN NOTHING?

394
00:20:22,155 --> 00:20:27,060
HE SHATTERED MY SHOULDER
WITH BUT A GLANCING BLOW.

395
00:20:28,328 --> 00:20:30,897
THE RIVER. I MUST JUMP IN.

396
00:20:30,997 --> 00:20:31,898
( groans )

397
00:20:34,467 --> 00:20:37,203
( blood flowing )

398
00:20:37,237 --> 00:20:38,471
Creature: IT'S ODD.

399
00:20:38,539 --> 00:20:40,974
I WAS DRINKING
THROUGH THE NIGHT,

400
00:20:41,041 --> 00:20:43,910
BUT SUDDENLY
I GOT SUCH A BRUTAL THIRST.

401
00:20:43,977 --> 00:20:46,680
Dio: MY BLOOD, HE'S DRAINING IT.

402
00:20:49,516 --> 00:20:50,684
WHAT THE...

403
00:20:51,652 --> 00:20:54,521
SO THIS IS
THE SECRET OF THE MASK.

404
00:20:54,588 --> 00:20:56,056
I'M DYING.

405
00:20:56,089 --> 00:20:58,091
( screams )

406
00:21:00,601 --> 00:21:03,003
NO! I HAD SUCH PLANS!

407
00:21:03,069 --> 00:21:06,673
MUST MY LAST SIGHT ON EARTH
BE THIS DAMNABLE SUNRISE?!

408
00:21:12,779 --> 00:21:16,917
( creature screams )

409
00:21:23,957 --> 00:21:27,293
Dio: THE SUN DESTROYED HIM.

410
00:21:27,393 --> 00:21:30,296
♪

411
00:21:38,271 --> 00:21:40,206
( thunder rumbling )

412
00:21:48,381 --> 00:21:50,250
WHAT'S THE MEANING OF THIS?

413
00:21:50,316 --> 00:21:52,152
WHY'S IT SO BLOODY DARK?

414
00:21:52,218 --> 00:21:53,253
( match strikes )

415
00:21:55,455 --> 00:21:56,723
JOJO.

416
00:21:56,790 --> 00:21:58,992
JoJo: YOU'RE A POISONER,
DIO BRANDO.

417
00:21:59,059 --> 00:22:01,735
I HAVE ALL THE PROOF
I REQUIRE AND THEN SOME.

418
00:22:01,802 --> 00:22:03,504
( Dio gasps )

419
00:22:03,604 --> 00:22:05,739
♪

420
00:22:21,522 --> 00:22:24,691
♪ I'LL BE THE ROUNDABOUT

421
00:22:24,791 --> 00:22:28,529
♪ THE WORDS
WILL MAKE YOU OUT AND OUT ♪

422
00:22:28,629 --> 00:22:33,867
♪ I SPEND THE DAY YOUR WAY

423
00:22:33,934 --> 00:22:36,369
♪ CALL IT MORNING
DRIVING THROUGH THE SOUND ♪

424
00:22:36,436 --> 00:22:41,274
♪ AND IN AND OUT THE VALLEY

425
00:22:48,515 --> 00:22:51,852
♪ THE MUSIC DANCE AND SING

426
00:22:51,885 --> 00:22:55,556
♪ THEY MAKE THE CHILDREN
REALLY RING ♪

427
00:22:55,622 --> 00:23:00,827
♪ I SPEND THE DAY YOUR WAY

428
00:23:00,894 --> 00:23:03,504
♪ CALL IT MORNING
DRIVING THROUGH THE SOUND ♪

429
00:23:03,570 --> 00:23:07,473
♪ AND IN AND OUT THE VALLEY

430
00:23:07,541 --> 00:23:11,044
♪ IN AND AROUND THE LAKE

431
00:23:11,077 --> 00:23:13,413
♪ MOUNTAINS COME
OUT OF THE SKY ♪

432
00:23:13,514 --> 00:23:15,749
♪ AND THEY STAND THERE

433
00:23:17,918 --> 00:23:20,386
♪ ONE MILE OVER,
WE'LL BE THERE ♪

434
00:23:20,420 --> 00:23:22,255
♪ AND WE'LL SEE YOU

435
00:23:24,658 --> 00:23:28,862
♪ 10 TRUE SUMMERS, WE'LL BE
THERE AND LAUGHING, TOO ♪

436
00:23:31,064 --> 00:23:34,000
♪ 24 BEFORE, MY LOVE,
YOU'LL SEE ♪

437
00:23:34,067 --> 00:23:38,271
♪ I'LL BE THERE WITH YOU

438
00:23:39,372 --> 00:23:40,707
♪

439
00:23:40,774 --> 00:23:43,009
Dio: JOJO, I'VE BEEN A DEVIL,

440
00:23:43,076 --> 00:23:44,945
BUT GRANT ME THIS ONE WISH.

441
00:23:45,045 --> 00:23:47,280
Man: THIS FELLOW REEKS
OF BRIMSTONE AND BLOOD.

442
00:23:47,347 --> 00:23:50,283
Dio: YOU SEE, I AM ABOUT
TO BECOME SO MUCH MORE!

443
00:23:50,350 --> 00:23:51,885
JoJo: DIO!

